<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cloud Engineer Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f9; }
        header { background: #232f3e; color: #fff; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px; }
        .card { background: #fff; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h2 { color: #232f3e; border-bottom: 2px solid #ff9900; display: inline-block; }
        .status { color: #2ecc71; font-weight: bold; }
        footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Cloud Deployment Project</h1>
        <p>Successfully hosted on AWS via Nginx</p>
    </header>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>This page is being served from an <strong>EC2 Instance</strong> running inside a custom <strong>VPC</strong>. This project demonstrates proficiency in cloud networking, security groups, and web server configuration.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>Technical Stack</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Cloud:</strong> AWS (VPC, Subnets, IGW)</li>
            <li><strong>Web Server:</strong> Nginx</li>
            <li><strong>OS:</strong> Amazon Linux 2 / Ubuntu</li>
            <li><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status">Live & Operational</span></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Deployed in 2026 | Built with Precision</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>